{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-chapter-level-2-chapter-level-2-tsx","path":"/topics/colic-infantile/background-information/causes/","result":{"pageContext":{"chapter":{"id":"8cfc6ae8-74a7-546a-b319-c166dac66e7b","slug":"causes","fullItemName":"Causes","depth":2,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field 9b78187f-821e-4f7a-b78b-53b715a95dde --><h2>What causes it?</h2><!-- end field 9b78187f-821e-4f7a-b78b-53b715a95dde -->","summary":"","htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item 71b344b5-9ae2-48fb-8499-10c857155995 --><!-- begin field 97f78dcf-dd49-40be-b758-77972df6b317 --><p><strong>The exact underlying cause of infantile colic is not known, and some commentators suggest it may reflect part of the normal distribution of infant crying</strong> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/colic-infantile/references/\">Akhnikh, 2014</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/colic-infantile/references/\">Lucassen, 2015</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/colic-infantile/references/\">Wolke, 2017</a>]<strong>. Other possible causes include:</strong></p><ul><li>Abnormal gastrointestinal motility and pain signals from sensitized pathways in the gut viscera.</li><li>Inadequate amounts of lactobacilli and increased amounts of coliform bacteria in the intestinal microflora, which influence gut motor function and gas production.</li><li>Psychosocial factors, such as family tension; parental anxiety; inadequate parent-infant interaction; overstimulation of the infant, or misinterpretation of crying.</li></ul><p>[<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/colic-infantile/references/\">NICE, 2011</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/colic-infantile/references/\">DTB, 2013</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/colic-infantile/references/\">Akhnikh, 2014</a>; <a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/colic-infantile/references/\">Vandenplas, 2015a</a>]</p><!-- end field 97f78dcf-dd49-40be-b758-77972df6b317 --><!-- end item 71b344b5-9ae2-48fb-8499-10c857155995 -->","topic":{"id":"e728c26a-005e-5e2a-9f46-f7dfec2cd36d","topicId":"254c369e-40fc-4169-bb92-30394399e7a4","topicName":"Colic - infantile","slug":"colic-infantile","lastRevised":"Last revised in June 2017","chapters":[{"id":"7a1f51d7-41cf-55a8-b71c-4d46909d5b0d","fullItemName":"Summary","slug":"summary","subChapters":[]},{"id":"9d366893-0b5e-5935-a891-e27308683472","fullItemName":"Have I got the right topic?","slug":"have-i-got-the-right-topic","subChapters":[]},{"id":"92f7cd8e-be30-5c7a-9859-062f74d2fd76","fullItemName":"How up-to-date is this topic?","slug":"how-up-to-date-is-this-topic","subChapters":[{"id":"29f83c05-485a-5dfe-9c41-548aa53dac7e","slug":"changes","fullItemName":"Changes"},{"id":"74255d9b-c133-5715-b340-d8bcf73ede99","slug":"update","fullItemName":"Update"}]},{"id":"b8fa0a59-acfb-55c8-9dcd-622a14e70f4e","fullItemName":"Goals and outcome measures","slug":"goals-outcome-measures","subChapters":[{"id":"85fb7ab5-907c-53bb-9341-53b717308830","slug":"goals","fullItemName":"Goals"},{"id":"3f55b4fd-1c0a-517f-8936-e05ef8f1c1f4","slug":"outcome-measures","fullItemName":"Outcome measures"},{"id":"2684a3a6-6535-5c17-9352-e8dfae930813","slug":"audit-criteria","fullItemName":"Audit criteria"},{"id":"8fc37b28-2832-51b0-8068-54d4b3ba6bf1","slug":"qof-indicators","fullItemName":"QOF indicators"},{"id":"d9fff9d3-37f5-5235-a336-f9a5c34ad1f5","slug":"qipp-options-for-local-implementation","fullItemName":"QIPP - Options for local implementation"},{"id":"464b9f75-1b8f-55fe-883e-0c2cee1438f9","slug":"nice-quality-standards","fullItemName":"NICE quality standards"}]},{"id":"3f35ca43-b738-5669-a5e1-7b965e35c7ff","fullItemName":"Background information","slug":"background-information","subChapters":[{"id":"e56f6e18-7e9b-502b-aa32-a45635f54cb0","slug":"definition","fullItem